name: KATE MOROSS X ADIDAS
description:
Kate Moross x Adidas Baltic Cup
Olympic Pack

Grey/Ice Grey

Exclusive KM pack comes with signed shoe box, a pair of Baltic sneakers, three extra pairs of coloured laces, a red KM triangle necklace and a green triangle keyring.

One pair available in each size while stocks last.
UK sizes: 6, 7, 8, 9, 10

"Kate Moross’s reworking of the Baltic Cup subtly marries her love of geometry with the iconic Olympic ring colors. Using premium suede gray uppers with trademark triangle motifs in an ingeniously reflective material, the young illustrator, filmmaker and designer from London manages to give these handball court shoes an updated sleek minimalist feel. A bright red loop tag on the tongue and matching green fabric loop at the heel completes the shoe."
- Hypebeast


The shipping price in your basket will automatically be for Special Delivery (signed for). This item is of high value and we want to make sure it gets to you safely, whatever country you are in.

name: ISO04 APES & ANDROIDS // GOLDEN PRIZE & RIVERSIDE
description: The first EVER record by this insane NYC find, that we picked up and became family with this summer.  We were saturated by their mind bending flexibility to sound like themselves and 50 of our favorite musical legends at the same time.  Lots of people have just cottoned on, and you can read reviews by the likes of Rolling Stone, and Pitchfork. For now, I sit and rub my hands together, hunched over the best 4 colour record sleeve I have ever designed, as if its my crystal ball, knowing that this band are going to make it, and in a MASSIVE way.  The larger print run and lower price is only because we didn’t want to be selfish, and want as many people in the universe to own this soon to be bands first vinyl press. Buy it here.

name: ISO03 MIDNIGHT JUGGERNAUTS // INTO THE GALAXY
description: Rare black card stock spined case with midnight black foil imprint, 4 panel pull out Kate Moross for Midnight Juggernauts debossed midnight foil artist print on black card.  Heavyweight Vinyl 7” with black paper inners. Tracks include Into the Galaxy Original and Architecture In Helsinki B side remix.
